{"tid":1318773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"V煞：面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。","createTime":"2019-07-15T04:21:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T05:15:29.000Z","uid":58335,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"81b5870447e4858e331297c3d5e3c985062ca2f6","tid":1318773,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:21:52.000Z","msg":"1. 面具之下只是個血肉之軀，而在這面具之下的，還有一個理念，只不過，理念，是刀槍不入的。<br />\n<br />\n（Beneath this mask there is more than flesh. Beneath this mask there is an idea, Mr.Creedy, and ideas are bulletproof..）<br />\n<br />\n2.我們的尊嚴可能不值錢，但它卻是我們唯一真正擁有的東西。它是我們最後一寸領地，但在那一寸領地里，我們是自由的。<br />\n<br />\n（Our integrity sells for so little, but it is all we really have. It is the very last inch of us, but within that inch, we are free）<br />\n<br />\n3.人民不應該害怕他們的政府，政府應該害怕它的人民。<br />\n<br />\n（People should not be afraid of their governments. Governments should be afraid of their people.）<br />\n<br />\n4.就算政府擁有的武力統治不讓人民發言，自由的言論仍然充滿着強大的力量。<br />\n<br />\n（the truncheon may be used in lieu of conversation, words will always retain their power)<br />\n<br />\n5.恐懼往往是政府的終極武器。<br />\n<br />\n（Fear became the ultimate tool of this government）<br />\n<br />\n6.力量來自團結，團結來自信念<br />\n<br />\n（Strength through unity, unity through faith）<br />\n<br />\n7.藝術家用謊言揭露真相，政治家用謊言掩蓋真相。<br />\n<br />\n（Artists use lies to tell the truth, while politicians use them to cover the truth up.）"},{"pid":"9ca3043ca58e21d80013ecacf960835bf06c0414","tid":1318773,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f93379daf62be87d58d0e4e4749a0e75af73de2d","tid":1318773,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ca3043ca58e21d80013ecacf960835bf06c0414","tid":1318773,"uid":11804,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:24:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"三毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/no